text: Countess Augusta Caroline Sophie Reuss-Ebersdorf was the Duchess of Saxe- Coburg-Saalfeld by marriage. She was born in Saalburg-Ebersdorf. She was the maternal grandmother of Queen Victoria and the paternal grandmother of Albert, Prince Consort.
